TopicTitle: STS-107 KSO Space Shuttle Misssion Series! Sending a Probe to Duna

Articles.Content:
The Seventh of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and Third Flight of the Tenacious! STS 107's objectives are to deploy the Duna Scout Probe, a test for a future manned landing attempt, return to the KSC runway, and land the probe on the surface of Duna!

Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing, while some is at 8x.

STS 108 Will bring up the KSO Space Station Core.
